name: COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Tyrone WIGGINS, Petitioners

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 28th day of January, 2014, the Petition for Leave to File Petition for Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc is GRANTED. Counsel is directed to file a Petition for Allowance of Appeal Nunc Pro Tunc within 30 days of this order.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.

COMMONWEALTH of Pennsylvania, Respondent v. Tyrone WIGGINS, Petitioners.

Jan. 28, 2014.
